description:
Minecraft custom map. Pause is back from vacation so Team Canada reunites once again to take on another CTM map (Complete The Monument). Diversity 3 is a highly polished and super fancy Minecraft adventure map which focuses on providing a diverse set of mini-games, each providing a unique challenge and varied gameplay.
